Hitting the Enter while focussed on a select list should submit the form

This can be done (although not for all browsers) by catching the enter key when focussed on the select lists and submitting the parent form. While this is "non-standard" in that browsers don't do this by default, it's quite consistent with the rest of the UI experience.

