If JIRA's workflow tool had more example workflows to choose from when starting out, users could get up to speed adapting JIRA's workflow to their environments quicker and also better understand what is considered good workflow practice. Some examples might include technical projects, business projects, etc.

Speak to Ben to discuss the templates when creating these.

